Minimal yet stylish, this orange kurta from Sangria is designed to set you apart from the rest. Tailored from cotton, this kurta has a split neckline, 3/4th&nbsp;sleeves and an A-line cut that gives a sharp look, while the floral block print all over makes it visually appealing as well as stylish. This kurta can be styled with a pair of black palazzos and brown sandals to look your best.   Split neckline Floral block print all over A-line cut Short button placket&nbsp; 
This model (height  5'8") is wearing size S
